          <h2 id="how-to-compress-a-pdf" class="heading-l">How to compress a PDF</h2><p>Follow these easy steps to learn how to make a PDF smaller:</p></div><div class="how-to-media how-to-media-large"><span class="modal-img-link"><picture>
