            <div class="text-content">
              <p class="icon-area"><picture><img loading="lazy" src="/dc-shared/assets/images/shared-images/frictionless/seo-icons/s-illu-trusted-pdf-tools-42.svg" alt="An Adobe Acrobat PDF document"></picture></p>
              <h3 id="adobe-pdf-compression-you-can-trust" class="heading-s">Adobe: PDF compression you can trust</h3>
              <p class="body-m">As the creators of the PDF, Adobe continues to innovate with high-quality PDF tools. Compress your PDFs with confidence when you use Adobe Acrobat.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
